# Frontend — Skills & Conventions

## Before writing

Read relevant area docs before modifying frontend code.

## Core skill

**[SKILL_FRONTEND]** — always active for frontend work.

## Conditional skills (activate by trigger)

[FRONTEND_SKILLS_LIST]

## Agents

- **ui-reviewer** — invoke when creating new pages or modifying existing UI
  - Modes: `review` (report only) or `fix` (report + corrections)
- **doc-updater** — invoke if changes are multi-area

## After modifying, update

Update frontend area doc in the same act if the change is architectural.
